# Design System

This is a **birthday invitation site for Alyssa**. Event copy lives in Supabase via `lib/invitation.ts`.

## Stack

- Tailwind CSS v4 utility-first styling only — no inline `style`, no per-component `.css` files
- Adapt [Tailwind UI](https://tailwindui.com) marketing patterns (rounded-full buttons, card shadows, spacing scale). Build with our tokens; do not paste Tailwind UI source verbatim.

## Colors

Always use theme tokens — never hardcode hex in JSX:

| Token | Usage |
|-------|-------|
| `blush` | Page background |
| `pink-light` | Cards, section surfaces |
| `rose` | Primary buttons, highlights |
| `gold-light` | Borders, secondary accents |
| `gold` | Headings, icons, emphasis |
| `ink` | Body text |

Examples: `bg-blush`, `text-gold`, `border-gold-light`, `bg-rose`

## Typography

- Headings: `font-display` (Playfair Display)
- Body: `font-sans` (Lato)

## Accessibility

- Interactive elements need `aria-label` when text alone is insufficient
- Support keyboard navigation (`tabIndex`, `onKeyDown` for custom controls)
- Visible focus: `focus-visible:outline-none focus-visible:ring-2 focus-visible:ring-gold focus-visible:ring-offset-2 focus-visible:ring-offset-blush`

## Layout

- **Mobile-first is mandatory** — base styles target phones (320–430px); enhance at `sm:` / `md:` only
- Use `Container` for max-width rhythm; use `Section` for vertical spacing
- No dark mode — light elegant palette only

## Mobile-first checklist

- Single column by default; no side-by-side until `sm:` or `md:`
- Touch targets min `44px` (`min-h-11`, `py-3`)
- Body text min `text-base` (16px)
- Primary CTAs: `fullWidth` on `Button` → `w-full sm:w-auto`
- Typography scales up: e.g. `text-4xl sm:text-5xl md:text-6xl`
- Images: `aspect-square object-cover`, no horizontal overflow
